&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/slh-logo-150-x-150px-for-online-white-background.png&quot;&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;alignnone  wp-image-5191&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/slh-logo-150-x-150px-for-online-white-background.png&quot; alt=&quot;slh-logo-150-x-150px for online white background&quot; width=&quot;79&quot; height=&quot;79&quot; /&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;alignnone  wp-image-5193&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/HUPFOCB_30311569_Pool_bar_600x399_72dpi-300x199.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;HUPFOCB_30311569_Pool_bar_600x399_72dpi&quot; width=&quot;112&quot; height=&quot;79&quot; /&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;alignnone  wp-image-5194&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/HUBODCV_56214438_Chateau_Des_Vigiers_1200x800_72dpi-300x200.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;HUBODCV_56214438_Chateau_Des_Vigiers_1200x800_72dpi&quot; width=&quot;106&quot; height=&quot;79&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;alignnone  wp-image-5189&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/HUSXRKH_60315458_Snow_Laden_Winter_180x270_72dpi-Resized.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;HUSXRKH_60315458_Snow_Laden_Winter_180x270_72dpi - Resized&quot; width=&quot;113&quot; height=&quot;79&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt; Welcome to Small Luxury Hotels of the World &amp;#8211; an unrivaled selection of some of the world&rsquo;s finest small independent hotels.&lt;br /&gt;
Diners Club International is excited to partner with Small Luxury Hotels of the World (SLH) to bring our cardmembers very special offers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Packed full of contemporary works of art by world-famous artists, Byblos Art Hotel Villa Amista is a grand, classic Venetian-style villa sitting in a beautifully manicured five-acre garden. Inside, ultra modern design by renowned architect and designer, Alessandro Mendini, stands out in stark contrast to the historic building. Expect statement design, a superb spa, fitness room, outdoor pool and exquisite cuisine. The newly opened OASI Relax outdoor area has two Jacuzzis and provides guests with the ultimate in outdoor relaxation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Offer 1: Elite Status in The Club, SLH&amp;#8217;s loyalty program&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Before making a reservation, it is important to &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/partners/dcinternational/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;visit Small Luxury Hotels of the World&amp;#8217;s website&lt;/a&gt; and follow the link to join The Club&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Enjoy a one-year complimentary membership as a Loved Member, with benefits including:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Priority &amp;amp; complimentary room upgrade on every stay (subject to availability at check-in)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complimentary daily continental breakfast for two&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Late check-out on every stay (subject to availability at check-in)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to exclusive Club rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to Club Concierge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Take advantage of the elite status offer by using rate code&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;SLHDCI15&lt;/strong&gt; (only necessary when reserving by phone)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Offer 2: Three Nights for the Price of Two&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy a complimentary 3rd night when you stay two consecutive nights at participating SLH properties around the world.&lt;br /&gt;
This offer will be presented on Privileges only for participating hotels.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;em&gt;There are c&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;urrently over 70 such properties participating in the complimentary night offer.&lt;br /&gt;
See the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/luxury-hotel-offers/diners-3-for-2/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;full list of participating hotels&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Take advantage of the complimentary 3rd night offer by using rate code N3RC&lt;/strong&gt; (only necessary when reserving by phone)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reservations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;After you &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/partners/dcinternational/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;register for the Loved status&lt;/a&gt;, you will receive a Loved membership number via email. You will receive a membership card after your first stay at a Small Luxury Hotels property.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Visit the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/hotels/byblos-art-hotel-villa-amista/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;hotel&amp;#8217;s website&lt;/a&gt; to make a reservation for this hotel or call SLH (visit the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/contact-us/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Contact Us page&lt;/a&gt; to find your local number) and provide rate code &lt;strong&gt;SLHDCI15&lt;/strong&gt; (only necessary when reserving by phone)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: #293033;&quot;&gt;Terms &amp;amp; Conditions&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #293033;&quot;&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;omplimentary night offer is subject to availability and is available on stays until August 31, 2016. Diners Club cardmembers members must stay at least two consecutive paid nights to receive the complimentary third night. The free night is reflected in the total price. Blackout dates may apply and during high demand certain room types may be limited. Rates are subject to local taxes and service charges. Prepayment/deposit with your Diners Club card is required at time of booking. This amount is non-refundable in the event of cancellation or change of dates of stay. The offer is non-transferable, non-combinable and valid for new bookings only. Please refer to &lt;a title=&quot;SLH's Terms &amp;amp; Conditions&quot; href=&quot;http://www.slh.com/club/terms-and-conditions/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;SLH&amp;#8217;s Terms &amp;amp; Conditions&lt;/a&gt; for more information.&lt;/p&gt;

